<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.263421>
    dc:description "PLATE 120. Lissodrillia arcas, new species. Fig. 1: holotype, NNW of Arcas Cays, Campeche Bank, Mexico, ventral, lateral & dorsal views (DMNH 46224). Figs. 2 – 6: paratypes, all from the type locality, ventral views. Fig. 2: ANSP 323999; Fig. 3: MCZ 279174; Figs. 4: UF 21573; Fig. 5: DMNH 107187; Fig. 6: MCZ 279174." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/263421/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

